    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2020 sedan in mint condition. The exterior is free of scratches, dents, or blemishes. Mechanically sound with no known issues and all systems functioning as expected. The interior shows no signs of wear \u2014 upholstery, trim, and surfaces are all in like-new condition. Low mileage and well-maintained throughout its ownership.",
